Insider Activity


Individual




Sotirios J. Vahaviolos



Dr. Sotirios J. Vahaviolos is a Member at American Society for Nondestructive Testing, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at MISTRAS Group, Inc. and Member-International Committee at Nondestructive Testing Management Association. Dr. Vahaviolos was previously employed as a Member by Acoustic Emission Working Group and a Consultant by Bell Laboratories. He received his undergraduate degree from Fairleigh Dickinson University, a graduate degree from Fu Foundation School of Engineering & Applied Science and a doctorate degree from Fu Foundation School of Engineering & Applied Science.



