 Dennis M. BertolottiPresident and Chief Operating Officer of MISTRAS Group


 
	Dennis Bertolotti is the President and Chief Operating Officer of MISTRAS Group. Mr. Bertolotti has been with MISTRAS since MISTRAS acquired Conam Inspection Services in 2003, where Mr. Bertolotti was a Vice President at the time of the acquisition. Mr. Bertolotti has been in the NDT business for over 25 years, and previously held ASNT Level III certifications and various American Petroleum Institute certifications, and received his Associate of Science degree in NDT from Moraine Valley Community College in 1983. Mr. Bertolotti received a Bachelor of Science and MBA from Otterbein College.













































